def_cn: 没有污渍的；没有污点的；没有疤痕的；没有斑点的
def_en: Something that is unmarked has no marks on it.

def_cn: 没有标记的；没有标志的
def_en: Something that is unmarked has no marking on it which identifies what it is or whose it is.

def_cn: （球类比赛中）无人防守的，没被注意到的
def_en: In a sport such as football, hockey, or basketball, if a player is unmarked, there are no players from the opposing team who are watching them in order to challenge them when they have control of the ball.
